<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth"><head><meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CLIMB | The GEM Method</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
