    <!-- The Problem Section -->
    <section id="problem" class="py-32 px-6 relative">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-start">
                <div class="sticky top-32">
                    <span class="text-[#B76E79] font-bold text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 block">The Pattern</span>
                    <h2 class="md:text-6xl leading-[1.1] md:p-8 text-5xl text-[#121212] tracking-tight font-serif rounded-sm mb-8 px-6 py-6 shadow-sm">
                        Functioning on the outside. <br>
                        <span class="italic text-[#121212]/70">Struggling on the inside.</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg font-normal text-[#121212] mb-12">
    For years, you did "all the right things." You worked hard. You pushed through. But underneath, you notice patterns of self-doubt and emotional suppression.
</p>
                    
                    <div class="border-l border-[#121212] pl-8 py-2">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-serif italic text-[#121212] mb-4">
                            "You can't think your way into safety."
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-[0.65rem] text-[#B76E79] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">— Gem</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="pt-4 space-y-20">
                    <div class="group md:p-10 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#B76E79]/20 transition-all duration-500 bg-[#D5C4A8] border-[#121212]/5 border rounded-sm pt-8 pr-8 pb-8 pl-8 shadow-sm">
    <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#121212]/10 rounded-full mb-6 text-[#B76E79] bg-[#F6F1EA] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:shield-warning-linear" width="20" height="20" stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
    </div>
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif text-[#121212] mb-4 tracking-tight">
        The Body Said "Stop"
    </h3>
    <p class="text-[#121212]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
        When the nervous system is dysregulated, we lose access to presence — and identity collapses into old patterns. A body holding stress long after the mind says "I'm fine" is not broken, it is protecting you.
    </p>
</div>

                    <div class="group relative z-20 bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-sm border border-[#121212]/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#B76E79]/20 transition-all duration-500">
    <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#121212]/10 rounded-full mb-6 text-[#B76E79] bg-[#F6F1EA] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:refresh-circle-linear" width="24" height="24" stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
    </div>
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif text-[#121212] mb-4 tracking-tight">
        The Solution
    </h3>
    <p class="text-[#121212]/70 leading-relaxed text-lg font-light">
        You have to regulate your way into safety. Through blending science-based physiology, somatic tools, and nervous system regulation, you can clear emotional charge and return to grounded self-leadership.
    </p>
</div>

                    <div class="p-12 bg-[#121212] text-[#F6F1EA] shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm mt-10">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain opacity-10"></div>
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-12 opacity-20">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:gem-linear" width="128" height="128" stroke-width="0.5"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>

                        <div class="relative z-10">
                            <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif italic mb-6 text-white tracking-tight">
                                Come back to yourself
                            </h3>
                            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80 mb-10 text-[#CFC8BE] text-lg font-light">
                                CLIMB is here to help you come back to yourself in minutes, not months. Regulate the body. Return to presence.
                            </p>
                            <div class="inline-block border border-[#B76E79] px-6 py-3 text-[0.65rem] font-semibold text-[#B76E79] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-[#B76E79] hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-default">
                                Regulation over Reaction
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The GEM Method Section -->
    <section class="overflow-hidden bg-[#F6F1EA] border-[#121212]/5 border-t pt-32 pr-6 pb-32 pl-6" id="gem-method">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mr-auto ml-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-24">
                <span class="text-[#B76E79] font-bold text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 block">The Methodology</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-[#121212] tracking-tight">The GEM Method</h2>
                <p class="text-[#121212]/60 mt-6 max-w-xl mx-auto font-light">
                    CLIMB is built on the first phase of the GEM Method.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Cards Container -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:gap-10 perspective-1000 gap-x-12 gap-y-12 items-center justify-center">
                
                <!-- Step 1: Growth - Adjusted to match size and alignment of other cards -->
                <div class="relative w-full max-w-[300px] aspect-[2/3] group cursor-pointer hover:-translate-y-3 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out z-20">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#121212] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518640467707-6811f4a6ab73?w=600&amp;q=80" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 mix-blend-luminosity scale-110 group-hover:scale-100 transition-transform duration-1000" alt="Background Texture">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#121212] via-transparent to-transparent opacity-90"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-x-4 top-4 bottom-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#B76E79] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#121212] shadow-lg shadow-[#B76E79]/20">
                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:leaf-bold" width="24" height="24"></iconify-icon>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-bold text-[#F6F1EA] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] border border-white/20 px-2 py-1 rounded-sm">Step 01</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-white leading-tight mb-2">Growth</h3>
                            <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#B76E79] mb-4"></div>
                            <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#B76E79] mb-3">Regulate the Body</h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-[#CFC8BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 font-light">
                                CLIMB guides your nervous system out of activation and into safety. This restores presence so you can access clarity again.
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#F6F1EA] group-hover:text-[#B76E79] transition-colors mt-6">
                                <span class="text-[0.65rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Included in CLIMB</span>
                                <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-right-linear" width="14" height="14"></iconify-icon>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 2: Empowerment -->
                <div class="anatomy-card relative w-full max-w-[300px] aspect-[2/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer hover:-translate-y-3 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain opacity-30 z-10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-3 border border-[#121212]/10 rounded-xl z-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 top-8 bottom-32 flex items-center justify-center p-6 z-0">
                         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757175-5700dde675bc?w=600&amp;q=80" class="anatomy-image w-full h-full object-contain opacity-70" alt="Identity">
                    </div>
                    <div class="z-30 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#D4C4A8] via-[#D4C4A8] to-transparent pt-8 pr-8 pb-8 pl-8 absolute right-0 bottom-0 left-0">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#121212]"></div>
                             <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-bold text-[#121212] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Step 02</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-serif text-[#121212] text-xl tracking-tight mb-2">Empowerment</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-[#121212]/70 leading-relaxed font-light">
                            
                            When your body feels safe, self-belief stabilizes. You reconnect to who you choose to be.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 3: Motivation -->
                <div class="anatomy-card relative w-full max-w-[300px] aspect-[2/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden group cursor-pointer hover:-translate-y-3 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain opacity-30 z-10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-3 border border-[#121212]/10 rounded-xl z-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 top-8 bottom-32 flex items-center justify-center p-6 z-0">
                         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=600&amp;q=80" class="anatomy-image w-full h-full object-contain opacity-70" alt="Action">
                    </div>
                    <div class="z-30 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#CFC8BE] via-[#CFC8BE] to-transparent pt-8 pr-8 pb-8 pl-8 absolute right-0 bottom-0 left-0">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#121212]"></div>
                             <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-bold text-[#121212] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Step 03</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-serif text-[#121212] text-xl tracking-tight mb-2">Motivation</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-[#121212]/70 leading-relaxed font-light">
                            
                            From regulation and presence, your next step becomes obvious. Action flows without force.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Method -->
